Quest_S15_Milestone_Cat_CompleteDailies_.Quest_S15_Milestone_Cat_CompleteDailies_: Congratulations. You're not a rat. Here's some hush money.
Don't tell anyone I'm here, and I'll make it worth your while.
I need a lookout. Can you handle it?
You're either trustworthy, or greedy. I can work with either.
Someone's spending Midas' gold. Bad idea.
When I find whoever did it... I suggest you don't watch.
I think they're on to me. Keep a sharp eye out.
You're still alive. That's the reward. But... I guess you earned a tip.
